    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>an hour after my last Letter went one came from y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                    friend <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Low</persName> of <placeName ref="pldb.xml#pl0701">Orkney</placeName> which
                    pleased me much he offers his service freely &amp; I dare say it will be of vast
                    use. he speaks of <bibl type="authorial">
                        <title ref="bi0058">a treatise of
                            his</title>
                    </bibl> that is soon to reach you. he permits me to have any
                    extracts which I shall be happy to have when it reaches you. Inclose a Letter
                    which I beg you would give my friend <persName ref="pe0018">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Jackson of the Post office</persName> begging
                    it may be sent by the first opportunity. if <bibl type="authorial">
                        <title ref="bidb.xml#bi0058">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Lows
                            treatise</title>
                    </bibl> is worth publishing I shall assist
                        <sic>cheerfull</sic>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>I am D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir <lb/>Truely y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232">T.Pennant</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <dateline>Dec<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 24<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi>
                    1772</dateline>

                <postscript>
                    <p>Pray let me know how the post goes to <placeName ref="pldb.xml#pl0701">the
                            Orknies</placeName>, &amp; when this sets out.</p>
                </postscript>

            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
